Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.12,0:09:57.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Welcome to ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense edition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.72,0:10:01.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Good evening, everyone!.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:05.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm Minori Suzuki, the voice of Ena Shinonome from Nightcord at 25:00.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.92,0:10:13.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This ProSeka AfterTalk is a program where we look back on the event while sharing the messages we've received from all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:16.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Today, we're covering the Colors of Pure Sense event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:20.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Did everyone enjoy the story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:22.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:25.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Between the fan festa and the movie stage greetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.84,0:10:30.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,the real-life cast events have been quite busy lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.54,0:10:35.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And then right after that, we have this N25 event, an Ena's focus event.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:39.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm sure it's been a bit of a whirlwind for everyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:42.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I hope you've been enjoying it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:49.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We've gathered your comments for this Aftertalk sent through email as well as the submissions channel on the Discord.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.68,0:10:52.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you all for your letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:58.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was so curious about what everyone had to say, I wanted to ask the staff to let me see all of them secretly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:04.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We'll go over some of your messages in our program today, so please look forward to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.94,0:11:11.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Also, please post your thoughts on the event or this broadcast using the hashtag #ProSekaAfterTalk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:17.93,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We'll also be watching the YouTube chat, so please keep all the messages coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:18.61,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.82,0:11:22.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Some people saying "I liked the story",
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:24.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I see some "{\i1}kon-niigo{\i0}"s too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.52,0:11:25.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes, {\i1}kon-niigo{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.48,0:11:37.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Also, there'll be an AfterLive for this event at 10PM, and the 3DMV for this event will be released at 10:05,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I'd like to watch that with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:44.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We'll try to stick to the schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.12,0:11:48.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\i1}but{\i0} I did want to spend a bit longer watching the story this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.40,0:11:53.86,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,I did ask staff if I could indulge myself on the story this time, so we'll spend a bit more time watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.86,0:11:56.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I hope you'll enjoy watching it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.32,0:12:05.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So with that, let's jump right into talking about the Colors of Pure Sense event story.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:09.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,How did you like the story, everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:14.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's look back together while going over some of the messages you've sent in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.08,0:12:19.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So actually, this is the first time I've done an AfterTalk since they got renewed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.44,0:12:22.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Last time I was here was a year ago, and that's around when the renewal happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:30.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I haven't gotten a chance to bring your thoughts into the story talk yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.24,0:12:32.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:35.16,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,This letter is from Amelia Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.16,0:12:36.82,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This is the first time I'm writing in!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:37.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:43.98,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"My favorite scene was the one where Ena deletes her selfie account."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.98,0:12:50.24,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Seeing her make the decision to stop running away and finally confront her art really showed how much she's grown."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:55.86,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Like Ena, I was also afraid of facing myself and kept running away,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.86,0:12:59.06,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but seeing Ena's positive attitude gave me the push I needed,"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:00.96,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"and made me want to do my best too."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:07.44,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Suzuki-san, what kind of feelings did you put into your performance of Ena this time?"
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:10.32,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,Thank you very much for the message.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:15.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That was a wonderful message, Amelia Time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.28,0:13:17.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.14,0:13:23.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'd like to talk more about it while watching the story later,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:36.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but something I'm more conscious of when acting as Ena, both in this event and when singing recent N25 songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:42.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,is her resolve to not go back to the old Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:46.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I personally kept that in mind because,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:57.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,even if the pace is slow, Ena is moving forward bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.15,0:14:04.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So while N25's songs often has negative or pessimistic lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:08.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and the music usually has a darker mood,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:11.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I tried not to make that the main thing in this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:18.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Like, maybe if were to I add just a hint of tearing up or a regretful tone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:24.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,that might make a line, or the song as a whole, stand out more to the listeners' ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.48,0:14:28.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So people might say "Oh, I like this part," or "that was nice, let me play that again."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.48,0:14:33.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Those kinds of lines would probably leave more of an impression on people's ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:41.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But that would just be my own desire for validation as Suzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:48.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I wanted to show Ena's gradual steps forward in both the songs and the story dialogue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:58.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So even with the same words, I wanted to make sure you could feel that she's moving forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.28,0:15:06.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And so thinking of the story too, I sang more positively as the song went on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:11.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's what I kept in mind while performing for this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.78,0:15:14.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And so... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.32,0:15:23.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,In this event and recent songs, she's realized that the world is warmer than she thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.18,0:15:28.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and she knows that the people around her will support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.68,0:15:31.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I made sure to reflect that in my performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.66,0:15:35.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, moving on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.06,0:15:39.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's read another message.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.24,0:15:42.98,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,This one is from Sudachi Udon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.98,0:15:44.42,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Hello, Minori-san."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.22,0:15:48.98,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I read through Colors of Pure Sense."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.98,0:15:50.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.06,0:15:58.30,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"What left an impression on me was the scene in Episode 7 where Ena gets so excited because she's having so much fun painting."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:04.28,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Ena previously could only feel validation from others, like with her selfie account,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:11.02,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but she finally realized, 'I'm fine just as I am. My world and the way I express myself can be as free as I want them to be.'"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.02,0:16:16.16,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"See Ena's world is gradually becoming more colorful and her eyes start to sparkle,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:22.08,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"all as she says drawing is fun. I connected with that moment thanks to your voice, Minori-san,"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:23.30,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"It moved me to tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:30.28,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"I want to continue watching over and supporting Ena, who has resolved not to give up on her art and her dreams."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.28,0:16:34.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,From Niyori-san... "Thank you so much for..." Oh, what a lovely message.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.88,0:16:41.78,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much bringing the colors of Ena's heart to life so vividly with your wonderful vocal performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.78,0:16:44.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm the one who should be thanking you for appreciating it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:53.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I always hope that Ena's feelings will reach everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:58.74,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Of course, she's a character in a game, a 2D character,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:00.65,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but Ena is truly alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:06.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And no one knows what her future holds yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:09.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I—how to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.54,0:17:15.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I really want to deliver something that feels real.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.92,0:17:18.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So thank you for such a kind message.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.83,0:17:19.57,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:29.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, I still have so much to talk about. If I just keep chatting here,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.04,0:17:32.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,it'll already be 10:05 and we'll have to skip watching the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So let's move right along.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:39.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've picked out some scenes I personally want to talk about,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so let's watch them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:44.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was a bit selfish today with the selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.92,0:17:48.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The staff are shaking their heads when I say "selfish,"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:48.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But um,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.50,0:17:54.90,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,, I actually really wanted to watch from Episode 1 to 8 with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.90,0:18:00.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But let's just watch Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.88,0:18:05.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This is an AfterTalk, so Minori will be be talking quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:06.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Minori, uh, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.82,0:18:14.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So if you think I'm yapping too much, please go back and watch the story in the game later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.34,0:18:17.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Episodes 7 and 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.32,0:33:39.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think she knew deep down all along.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.20,0:33:42.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Like, "I'm just avoiding it, aren't I?"
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.80,0:33:47.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ena's already made so many promises to herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.95,0:33:57.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so she knew she'd been using selfies as an escape or a crutch.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.72,0:34:00.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But she couldn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.00,0:34:01.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She wants to go to Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.56,0:34:08.95,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But she didn't have the resolve to tell those herself or those around her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.88,0:34:18.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But this time, she's telling herself "no, I {\i1}won't{\i0} run away," and "I {\i1}will{\i0} decide."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.80,0:34:26.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She knows it's not a smooth road ahead, but it feels like the fog in her heart has cleared.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.18,0:34:29.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(660,926)}She feels that relief, but also there's a lot ahead for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.72,0:34:31.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She feels that relief, but also there's a lot ahead for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.96,0:34:37.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I knew Ena had a lot on her mind about the road ahead,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.84,0:34:49.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I also knew that she felt a huge sense of relief after all this. So I acted with this both feelings in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.12,0:34:56.75,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The reason I chose Episodes 7 and 8 is because of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.75,0:35:04.25,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,They've been through a lot, and there were times she couldn't face him, but she really admires him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.25,0:35:07.35,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As she grew up a lot happened between them,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.35,0:35:11.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and he isn't the best with words, so she butted heads with him a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.45,0:35:26.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But as she grew as an artist, she started to remember those feelings of admiration for him she hid out of frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.22,0:35:31.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's why I got to voicing young Ena was so special.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.62,0:35:39.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As a child, she was so pure, and everything was new and sparkling.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.15,0:35:49.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And in that world was her father, and he was someone she looked up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.42,0:35:52.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Someone who creates amazing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.12,0:36:00.91,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I imagined Ena talking to him as just this mass of pure light.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.91,0:36:14.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I played that scene keeping in mind that feeling of wonder and delight Ena had for her father and the art he created.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.62,0:36:23.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And because of that, I could continue back into Ena's drawing scene keeping that same wonderful and sparkling feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.22,0:36:37.36,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Being able to draw with so much joy while embracing that feeling was a huge moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.12,0:36:41.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And for the first time, she could clearly say, "It's fun."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.22,0:36:47.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This is such an important point for Ena to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.54,0:36:50.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's still on her journey, but she finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.32,0:36:53.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And so— Oh, I'm gonna cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.08,0:36:59.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And so when— Ah, this is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.68,0:37:06.05,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,When I first saw the script at home, I cried so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.05,0:37:07.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was just so happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.54,0:37:10.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Wah! This is a total broadcast accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.42,0:37:17.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's been five years—well, not five years in Ena's timeline—
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.04,0:37:19.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but there's so been so much building up to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.12,0:37:24.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think many of you find Ena's story very relatable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.84,0:37:33.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Since I'm also in a world of art where there are no "correct" answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.15,0:37:34.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I really understand her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.50,0:37:43.15,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But more than that, seeing Ena's hard work finally start to pay off...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.15,0:37:45.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,well, "pay off" is a simple way to put it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.20,0:37:46.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.16,0:37:59.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was so happy that I cried for her as Minori Suzuki. I was like "Good for you!"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.24,0:38:04.24,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And while reading, I felt Ena's relief that she finally made it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.48,0:38:14.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She could finally feel this simple feeling. She's worked so hard to come to this point and finally let go of all that tension and angst.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.36,0:38:17.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry... I have plenty of tissues here.
Comment: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:23.64,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.12,0:38:23.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, I put all those feelings into acting and the tears just started flowing naturally.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.64,0:38:29.28,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There were parts where I got choked up and couldn't get the words out, but that's what acting is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.28,0:38:34.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That actually helps get across Ena's feelings though acting all the more.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.45,0:38:35.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Since I started crying—
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.82,0:38:39.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Since I started crying as Ena, I knew she was crying with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.52,0:38:43.67,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,They actually adjusted to my timing—
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.67,0:38:47.49,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So usually, you can click to advance the dialogue right as the line ends,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.49,0:38:57.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but they didn't cut any of the recording and let the pauses naturally hold before showing the next button. I'm so grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.54,0:39:05.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've received so many comments saying this was a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.30,0:39:12.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And it wasn't just about how my acting was, or how my voice sounded as Suzuki Minori.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.42,0:39:21.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Instead of focusing on me, everyone really took {\i1}Ena's{\i0} attitude and determination to heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.62,0:39:27.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So many people were glad for here, some felt encouraged to work hard too,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.38,0:39:33.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and long-time fans were just so glad to see her payoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.12,0:39:42.81,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even though her journey is just beginning, I'm so glad people care so much for Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.47,0:39:54.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I poured my absolute all into portraying Ena and how far she's come for this, so I'm really happy with how it turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.58,0:39:55.43,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.43,0:39:56.07,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.26,0:39:58.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, let's take a look at the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.56,0:40:07.05,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,By the way, I chose this one because it's the moment Ena finally sees a glimmer of hope after suffering so much for her art.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.05,0:40:07.75,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.34,0:40:15.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Let's spend about four minutes looking at the card illustrations together.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.18,0:40:23.38,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,Before that, I have some comments about the costumes to share from the illustration team.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.38,0:40:31.32,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"The theme of this story is Ena's struggle to get into art school,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.32,0:40:37.52,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,840)}"becoming discouraged after not getting the grades she was hoping for, but ultimately deciding not to quit."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.52,0:40:41.52,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"Our motif this time was an art apron over a school uniform,"
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:45.42,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"designed to capture Ena's look as a student preparing for entrance exams."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.42,0:40:52.64,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"While she's had had other apron outfits, this time we gave Ena a patched-up one."
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.64,0:41:00.14,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"This represents her persistence through repeated setbacks, fitting the themes from this specific story."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.14,0:41:06.16,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"We kept strong uniform elements like the sailor collar and pleats,"
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.16,0:41:09.92,DefaultOnibe,listener_mail,0,0,0,,"but modified the overall form to give it more of a costume feel."
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.92,0:41:12.66,DefaultOnibe,host_meta,0,0,0,,And this is the illustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.02,0:41:20.74,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And then the pre-trained version... everyone seemed to really like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.74,0:41:22.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She looks like she's having fun painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.50,0:41:23.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Her hands are all messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.78,0:41:25.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's so wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.30,0:41:36.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(656,908)}And here are the untrained and post-trained cards of everyone supported Ena through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.78,0:41:43.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Kanade is a creator herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.22,0:41:47.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so even though their genres are different, she understands Ena's feelings. And KAITO...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.80,0:41:54.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah, KAITO gave Ena so many important words of advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.94,0:42:01.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There's also that scene where they're eating ice cream. So I named the team "Frozen Yogurt."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.38,0:42:04.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,That's just because I personally love frozen yogurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:06.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,My desires are leaking through.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.14,0:42:07.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And here's Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.76,0:42:08.61,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.62,0:42:11.10,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So many lovely paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.14,0:42:13.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Look, they're eating ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.01,0:42:15.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.54,0:42:19.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And finally, Mafuyu— wait, oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.38,0:42:22.49,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ah, I can't long-press.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.49,0:42:23.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.62,0:42:25.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's holding the apron.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.14,0:42:26.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes, so adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.18,0:42:29.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.68,0:42:34.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So, you've seen the pre- and post-trained illustrations...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.94,0:42:36.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Oh, come on—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:36.30,0:42:38.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Anyway, those were the illustrations.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.58,0:42:44.85,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I have a few more minutes, so I'll talk a bit more about the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.85,0:42:50.06,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So, in one of the previous stories—I'm trying to remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.70,0:42:52.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Which was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.62,0:42:54.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The last one wasn't specifically about her art,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.82,0:43:01.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So I think it was the one before that, where we sang "I'm the Rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.98,0:43:05.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,During that story about Ena's drawing—"drawing" sounds a bit off.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.60,0:43:12.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,About her {\i1}painting{\i0}, I happened to visit an art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.62,0:43:21.07,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I got to understand how it felt to actually look at paintings, and through that, I was able to understand and act as Ena better.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.07,0:43:24.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But before this event story, I was just walking down the street,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.72,0:43:31.98,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,and I passed an actual art prep school, the kind Ena would attend. It was just right there on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.98,0:43:43.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I felt this intense tension just looking from the outside, and it reminded me how tough her world is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.82,0:43:46.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,And I put in those thoughts into the recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.34,0:43:57.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Every day, I try to act in a way that conveys the reality of the Ena's situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.62,0:43:58.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.41,0:43:59.97,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.97,0:44:02.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.88,0:44:03.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.64,0:44:07.40,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I still have a few dozen seconds left.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.76,0:44:13.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Some of you might have already seen the AfterLive by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.02,0:44:16.48,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It follows the content of Episode 8,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.16,0:44:22.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so you can see Ena's refreshed expression. Things will still be hard for her,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.52,0:44:27.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but I hope her resolve comes through in her expression and her singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.32,0:44:34.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I hope it's reaching all of you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.95,0:44:35.45,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:44:35.97,0:44:36.47,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.97,0:44:36.47,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.24,0:44:39.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Man, it really is a great story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.18,0:44:41.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Ena is so loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.58,0:44:43.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm so grateful we got such a wonderful story.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.62,0:44:50.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,With that said, I'd like to talk about the music after we watch the 3DMV that was written specifically for this event.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.18,0:44:51.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.88,0:45:11.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Breathing inside a borrowed life, in a body that can't become anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.12,0:45:21.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If I dive deep into the depths, the me from that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.52,0:45:26.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,is still smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.36,0:45:47.64,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Looking back, there were certainly fragments of dreams sprouting in my chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.36,0:46:00.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Pressed down by the weight of strings, they eventually turned into hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.24,0:46:08.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,There's no use in trying to stroke the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.92,0:46:20.20,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,This small, gentle light... my belief still won't reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.92,0:46:33.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even so, I want to draw more of the future with these hands on the white scenery before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.80,0:46:44.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Even if the past isn't beautiful, I'll be myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.28,0:46:49.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I just want to draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.88,0:46:55.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,this world that reflects in my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.57,0:47:04.52,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}And we're back. Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.52,0:47:06.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}My screen just popped up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.56,0:47:15.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}That was the 3DMV for the song Chouchou-P wrote for this event, titled "The Name of Your Drawing."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.24,0:47:21.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Wait, I got mixed up. That was the 3DMV for "The name of painting."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.52,0:47:22.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.76,0:47:26.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Should I do this first? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.36,0:47:32.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}For a second, I mixed up my own notes with Chouchou-P's comments.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.44,0:47:33.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I was like, "Wait, what?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.72,0:47:40.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Ok so, Let me read the notes I sent to the staff beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.56,0:47:46.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"Just listening to it evokes memories of Ena's long journey, and it brings me to tears."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.68,0:47:53.96,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"The title has her name in it, so I felt it was truly a song written for Ena."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.84,0:48:00.57,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"Embracing the regret and pain that she's felt along her journey, instead of just lamenting it,"
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.57,0:48:08.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}"I sang with the newfound optimism and determination she has to turn those feelings into strength."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.18,0:48:11.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}That's what past-me sent in to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.64,0:48:16.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Chouchou-P's actual comments were introduced on the ProSeka News Station and such.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.70,0:48:20.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}They should be on Twitter—I mean, X—as well, so please check them out.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:24.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But yeah, those were the feelings I put into the song.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.56,0:48:25.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.24,0:48:30.76,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}There are lyrics that feel like she's looking back at the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.28,0:48:35.12,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But it really is like the {\i1}current{\i0} Ena is the one doing the reflecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.76,0:48:40.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I'm sure Ena has regrets,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.04,0:48:44.66,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But I think she's a girl who understands that those regrets made her who she is today.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.66,0:48:55.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}So even for the phrases about the past, I didn't want to sing them with the pure regret of the old Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.62,0:49:01.84,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}So while embracing those feelings, I sang with her newer sense of resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.84,0:49:04.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Like I said during the story part,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.18,0:49:10.80,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I tried to include that sense of relief and the brightness of finally feeling the joy in painting again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.80,0:49:15.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}But also that this isn't the goal; it's a new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.46,0:49:24.54,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I was very conscious of capturing that duality while singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.54,0:49:30.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}So rather than a huge outburst or breakthrough of emotion,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.18,0:49:36.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}it's more like quietly reflection within myself to cheer myself on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.70,0:49:41.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Like patting my own chest and saying, "Let's do this."
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.72,0:49:46.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}That's the image I had in mind as I sang.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.32,0:49:48.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I just end up crying, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.58,0:49:52.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}I've already heard the full version, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.14,0:49:53.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,{\pos(666,992)}Since I'm the one who sang it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.56,0:49:54.68,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.68,0:49:57.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I just can't help but cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.04,0:49:58.82,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm just so hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.82,0:50:02.04,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Both this story and the song just make me tear up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.04,0:50:03.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,What am I going to do? What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.72,0:50:07.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I thought I wouldn't cry this time, but I did anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.06,0:50:08.92,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.92,0:50:15.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,To those of you who felt a bit jealous that I've heard the full version, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.70,0:50:22.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The 2DMV for this new song, "The Name of Your Drawing,"
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.22,0:50:27.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,will be uploaded to the official ProSeka YouTube channel at 10:15 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.62,0:50:31.72,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please check that out along with the 3DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.72,0:50:36.50,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If it's like the previous 2DMVs, that means you'll be able to hear the full version too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.18,0:50:40.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I haven't even seen the 2DMV myself yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.60,0:50:49.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Now, to give some belated thoughts on the 3DMV...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.18,0:50:52.44,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I sang the full song for the recording, but I knew how the lines were split,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.44,0:50:54.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,so I knew which parts would be Ena's.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.42,0:50:59.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,The song starts with the other three members of N25 singing one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.60,0:51:07.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So in the 3DMV inside my head—my imaginary 3DMV—it didn't start with Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.34,0:51:10.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I was wondering how it would actually begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.02,0:51:14.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Would all four, or rather five of them appear at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.32,0:51:18.62,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Or would it start with Mizuki, who has the first line?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.62,0:51:23.30,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But then I saw it was showing Ena for the whole opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.30,0:51:32.58,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm always happy when other characters get a lot of screen time for their fans, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.58,0:51:41.08,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But this MV put such a huge spotlight on Ena, and it matched the story so perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.08,0:51:46.32,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It really felt like it was capturing Ena's journey and current attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.32,0:51:51.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,As her voice actress, that made me so incredibly happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.26,0:52:04.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's always been like this, but Ena's commissioned songs always feel like she's getting closer and closer to the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.14,0:52:07.26,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Well, that's just my own otaku analysis.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.26,0:52:08.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,But things like that make me happy too.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.86,0:52:15.22,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I've only seen it a few times myself, so I want to sit down and watch it properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.22,0:52:17.71,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'm so excited for the 2DMV.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.71,0:52:18.35,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.50,0:52:24.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I think that's everything... I don't think I've left anything out.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.46,0:52:29.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Well, I've truly entrusted everything to Ena's voice.
Comment: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:37.78,DefaultOnibe,,0,0,0,,[autosub] Chunk boundary — review translation around this line
Dialogue: 0,0:52:29.78,0:52:37.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,More than anything, I hope you can feel Ena's thoughts and attitude through the music and the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.30,0:52:41.66,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Everyone, please continue to support Ena.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.66,0:52:44.42,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.94,0:52:47.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Though I may not Ena herself,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.38,0:52:55.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,but as the person who voices her, I feel like I'm someone close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.18,0:53:09.88,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,She's made a new resolution, and I'll work hard as an actress to express her growth, so please keep watching over her.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.88,0:53:11.34,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.34,0:53:18.38,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It's been a short time, but that's all for this ProSeka AfterTalk: Colors of Pure Sense edition.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.38,0:53:20.90,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,To everyone watching the stream, how did you like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.46,0:53:28.00,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,If you haven't finished the story for the Colors of Pure Sense event yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.00,0:53:31.14,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Did I look funny crying so much like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.42,0:53:38.02,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,You can read the whole thing from the Event Story menu once the next event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.02,0:53:39.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So please, give it a read.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.60,0:53:43.70,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,We're always looking for messages for our AfterTalks.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.70,0:53:51.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,You can submit them through the official ProSeka Discord channel or via email.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.86,0:53:56.78,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Please send one in when the next AfterTalk event starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.78,0:54:00.60,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Just make sure your messages are related to the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.60,0:54:03.71,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,It'd be a waste if I couldn't read it because it was about something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.71,0:54:04.46,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.46,0:54:08.18,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,In just about ten or twenty seconds...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.18,0:54:12.94,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,the 2DMV will be out, so let's watch it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.94,0:54:18.16,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,I'll watch it as soon as we close out here, so you should all check it out too.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.16,0:54:21.56,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,So with that, see you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.56,0:54:23.86,DefaultOnibe,host,0,0,0,,Goodbye!
